(64, 2, '2012-07-21 15:16:39', '2012-07-21 15:16:39', '<p style="text-align: center;">Are you at your Whit’s End with your career search?\r\nThen you have come to the right place for answers and help.\r\nWhat Career Resources do you need?\r\nWhere do you turn first? What is the first step you should take?\r\nWe will help you determine your next move and target your efforts and obtain the goal you are looking for.\r\nRemember, before you climb that Ladder of Success be sure it’s leaning against the correct wall.</p>', 'Blog', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'blog', '', '', '2012-09-05 02:47:00', '2012-09-05 02:47:00', '', 0, 'http://wecareerresources.com/?page_id=64', 0, 'page', '', 0),
