(28, 2, '2012-07-21 14:35:42', '2012-07-21 14:35:42', '<h4>Whit''s End Career Resources has helped in the following areas:</h4>\r\n<span style="font-size: small;">• Interview and assess job seekers and claimants’ skills, aptitudes and abilities.</br>\r\n• Evaluate job seekers and review their education,background and ability to obtain employment.</br>\r\n• Designed, planned and conducted weekly workshops for 1049 attendees on subjects such as; Job Search, Resumes, Interviews and Mock Interviewing, resulting in interviews for 857 of those who attended all four workshops and 749 of those were hired.</br>\r\n• Work with employers in Strafford and Rockingham Counties and community organizations to find candidates for new positions and manage job orders and post on NH Job Match System online.</br>\r\n• Appeared on local radio station WTSN AM 1270 to discuss the NH “Return To Work Program” live on air and take questions. Invited by NBC Affiliate, WCSH TV Channel 6 in Portland Maine to appear on their "207" show to discuss; Job Search, Resumes, and Interviewing.</br>\r\n• Performed one on one counseling sessions with veterans, job seekers and claimants to assist them in preparing resumes, job searches and interview skills and negotiating job offers.</br>\r\n• Recognized by the Commissioner of NH Employment Security in August 2010 for individual and weekly workshop training development for job seekers.</br>\r\n• Solicited by the Commissioner of NH Employment Security to provide strategies, ideas and script for orientation video created for the NH “Return To Work Program” shown at each office of NH Employment Security.</br>\r\n• Created PowerPoint presentations for the “Mature Worker”, “Resume”, “Job Search”, and “Do’s and Don’ts” of Interviewing” Workshops.</span>', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2012-08-28 14:25:21', '2012-08-28 14:25:21', '', 0, 'http://wecareerresources.com/?page_id=28', 0, 'page', '', 0),
